    "body": "Right that's because of this derivation:\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-react/blob/2122c5518f406e271c82785b025e619d32a86f34/nix/mobile/android/maven-and-npm-deps/default.nix#L30-L31\r\nSpecifically this part:\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-react/blob/2122c5518f406e271c82785b025e619d32a86f34/nix/mobile/android/maven-and-npm-deps/default.nix#L38-L48\r\nWhich means that all files contained in the `android` dir are part of this derivation. So every time something changes in it the derivation will be rebuilt.\r\n\r\nNow, if the XML files you are editing should have no effect on the node modules then we could exclude them from this derivation.",
